1 Byte to byte sync
2 逐一字节同步
1 Compare files "byte to byte". This option is not designed for normal sync operations, you should use it only in particular situations because it will slow down very much the sync.
2 "逐一字节"对比文件. 此选项不适用于普通同步操作, 你应该只在特定情况下使用它, 因为它会很大程度减慢同步速度.
1 This option is not designed for normal sync operations, you should use it only in particular situations,
furthermore, selecting ''Verify Byte to Byte'' will slow down very much the sync.

Are you sure to want enable this option?
2 此选项不适用于普通同步操作, 你应该只在特定情况下使用它, 此外, 选择"逐一字节校验"将会很大程度减慢同步速度.

你是否确认要启用这一选项?
