1 Syncronize folders using more recent files from both, you will obtain two equal folders with the more recent files of both
2 使用两边的较新文件同步文件夹, 你将获得两个相同的文件夹, 且其中均包含最新的文件
1 DSynchronize - Bidirectional Sync
2 DSynchronize - 双向同步
1 If Realtime is not enabled, Bidirectional sync can't get file deletions, because DSynchronize don't knows if a single file was added on source path or was deleted from destination path (or viceversa), so it assumes that all files was added everywhere.

This can give unattended results, do you want enable anyway Bidirectional Sync?
2 如果实时同步没有启用, 双向同步无法决定文件的删除, 因为DSynchronize不知道一个文件是在来源处被添加还是从目的地路径处被删除(或者反过来), 因此它假定所有的文件都是被添加的.

这可以提供无人值守的结果, 你是否真的要启用双向同步?
