# Help window --------------------------------------------------------------
1 DSynchronize - Help
2 DSynchronize - 帮助
1 Help
2 帮助
1 About
2 关于
1 [HOT KEYS]
F1 = Open this window.
F2 / Enter = Modify Paths.
Del = Delete Paths couple.
PagUp / PagDn = Move item up or down.
Right Click = Test Path, Set Filters, Browse Paths.
Alt+F4 = Exit program.
Alt+F5 = Exit program without save settings.
Right / Left = Switch between Sources and Destinations.
Up / Down = Select previous / next item.
Further Down = Add new couple of paths (Source and Destination).

[COMMAND LINE]
/START = Start synch with last saved options.
/STARTJOB "JobName" = Start synch with selected Job options).
/MINIMIZE = Starts minimized in the Tray Bar.
/HIDDEN = Do not display icon in Tray Bar.
/NOSECURITYCHECK  = Don't makes security check before sync.
/NOMONITORCHECK = Do not check monitor resolution.
/AUTOREALTIME = Starts minimized, do a standard sync and activate RealTime.
/SOMEFILE.INI  = Starts using selected INI file.
2 [热键]
F1 = 打开这个窗口.
F2 / 回车键 = 修改路径.
Del = 删除成对路径.
翻上页 / 翻下页 = 上移或下移项目.
右键 = 测试路径, 设置过滤器, 浏览路径.
Alt+F4 = 退出程序.
Alt+F5 = 退出程序且不保存设置.
左箭头 / 右箭头 = 互换来源和目的地.
上箭头 / 下箭头 = 选择上一个 / 下一个项目.
继续向下 = 添加新的成对路径(来源和目的地)

[命令行]
/START = 以最后保存的选项开始同步.
/STARTJOB "jobName" = 以选定的作业选项开始同步.
/MINIMIZE = 以最小化到系统托盘开始.
/HIDDEN = 不在系统托盘显示图标.
/NOSECURITYCHECK = 在同步前不做安全性检查.
/NOMONITORCHECK = 不检测显示器分辨率.
/SOMEFILE.INI = 使用选定的INI文件开始.
